  <brief_title>Effect of Liraglutide on Pulsatile Insulin Secretion in Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of NNC90-1170 on Pulsatile Insulin Secretion in Type 2 Diabetic Patients. A Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Randomised, Single-dose, Cross-over Trial</official_title>
