  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Europe. The aim of this trial is to assess the effect of NNC
      90-1170 (liraglutide) on pulsatile insulin secretion and insulin secretion after a standard
      meal in subjects with type 2 diabetes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
